ABUJA – Federal Capital Territory Ad­ministration (FCTA) on Tues­day debunked the story in one of the dailies that hospitals in the territory are currently rendering skeletal services due to the death of 20 medical doctors from COVID-19. The figure which is very far from the truth was cred­ited to the President of the FCT chapter of the Nigerian Medical Association, Dr Ene­mo Amodu. Although Amodu has since said that he was mis­quoted, as the 20 fatalities he gave was the national figure cutting across the 36 States of the Federation and the FCT. EXPOSED - HOW LAGOS DOCTOR DISCOVERED MAJOR REASONS WHY MOST WIVES NOW HEAVILY CHEATS ON THEIR HUSBANDS AND THE PERMANENT SECRET TO SEXUALLY SATISFYING THEIR WIVES. DON'T BE A VICTIM! A statement signed and made available to newsmen in Abuja by FCT Minister, Malam Muhammad Musa Bello Chief Press Secre­tary, Mr Anthony Ogunleye hinted that, it is still perti­nent that the FCTA sets the records straight in view of the fact public confidence in public health institutions is very essential in the face of the current public health emergency orchestrated by COVID-19. He said that the current situation in FCT hospitals as at Monday, 28th Decem­ber, 2020 are as follows: All FCT hospitals are operating at full capacity inclisive of emergencies for adults and children, delivery and ma­ternity services, theatre services (operating 24 hour services), laboratory and pharmaceutical services, and hospital kitchens. All clinics will resume full ser­vices after the Christmas holidays on Tuesday, 29th of December, 2020. COVID-19 Second Wave: 16 Out Of Every 100 Samples Tested Positive — FG Crossover Night: CAN Asks Churches To Close Services By 11p.m He said, “While there had been incidences where COVID-19 positive patients had infected some medical personnel, these personnel and indeed the patients have been treated and discharged and the affected hospital areas fully decontaminated without any adverse effect on the overall functionality of the hospitals. “Since the first case of COVID-19 was recorded in the FCT, a total of 476 health workers inclusive of doctors, nurses, pharmacists, labora­tory staff, drivers and other auxiliary personnel have been infected by the virus. Of these figure, a total of 4 doctors have succumbed to the disease, the latest, a fe­male doctor from Gwarimpa hospital passed on over the course of the week. There has not been any other recorded fatality of a health personnel over the last one week. SHOCKING! DOCTORS ARE MESMERIZED BY THIS NATURAL PREMATURE EJACULATION AND SMALL SIZE SOLUTION GUARANTEED TO BULLDOZE YOUR WOMAN INTO SEXUAL SUBMISSION